comments: Murray (DEN) continues forward after releasing the pass and incidental foot to foot contact occurs with Bridges (BKN) as they come together.
Dinwiddie (BKN) slightly extends his leg toward Murray (DEN) during the jump shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
Jokic (DEN) trails Bridges (BKN) and moves forwards into his body, initiating contact that affects his SQBR during the driving shot attempt.
Claxton (BKN) briefly places a hand to Jokic's (DEN) front and marginal contact occurs that does not affect his FOM.
Johnson (BKN) and Caldwell-Pope (DEN) mutually engage and disengage as marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Thomas' (BKN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Bridges (BKN) extends an arm into an airborne Watson's (DEN) body, initiating more than marginal contact during the driving shot attempt.
Watson (DEN) closes out toward Thomas' (BKN) jump shot attempt and makes body contact that affects Thomas' ability to return to the floor.
Smith Jr. (BKN) delivers contact to Murray (DEN) and dislodges him from his position.
Thomas (BKN) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN).
Murray (DEN) legally contests Thomas' (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) legally contests Bridges' (BKN) layup attempt.
Porter Jr. (DEN) extends a forearm into Johnson (BKN) and moves him off of his spot during the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) grabs and pulls Sharpe's (BKN) left arm, affecting his positioning for the rebound.  Sharpe does not initiate any illegal contact that dislodges Jokic from his position.
Claxton (BKN) commits a take foul on Gordon (DEN).
Finney-Smith (BKN) commits a take foul on Jokic (DEN).  The illegal contact occurs before Jokic enters his shooting motion.
